Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.57,0:01:35.53,Episode Title,EpTitle,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18\fad(939,1)}"My Cherished Feelings For You"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.67,0:01:42.55,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,D-Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.49,0:01:48.04,Main,Ornis,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to pummel you to \Nmy satisfaction, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.88,0:01:52.04,Main,Ornis,0000,0000,0000,,It appears that's unnecessary now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.68,0:01:56.22,Main,Ornis,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.02,0:02:22.06,Main,Ornis,0000,0000,0000,,No way?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.06,0:02:23.50,Main,Ornis,0000,0000,0000,,Why is his right arm—?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.50,0:02:25.88,Main,Ornis,0000,0000,0000,,No, more importantly, that form is—
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.19,0:02:31.58,Main,Ornis,0000,0000,0000,,I-I thought that was a counter-skill!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.59,0:02:42.60,Main,Hasegawa,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.27,0:02:54.64,Main,Hasegawa,0000,0000,0000,,You're pathetic, Ornis.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.64,0:02:56.61,Main,Ornis,0000,0000,0000,,Afleia-sama?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.87,0:03:00.81,Main,Hasegawa,0000,0000,0000,,Brynhildr was once the greatest Valkyrie,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.81,0:03:03.12,Main,Hasegawa,0000,0000,0000,,hunting down many souls for the chief god.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.12,0:03:07.16,Main,Hasegawa,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who recklessly \Nunleashed that sealed power.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.90,0:03:09.43,Main,Hasegawa,0000,0000,0000,,You brought this on yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.41,0:03:12.96,Main,Hasegawa,0000,0000,0000,,Did you want to kill Basara so\N badly that you'd go that far?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.54,0:03:15.16,Main,Ornis,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think I could forgive some fool
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.16,0:03:18.59,Main,Ornis,0000,0000,0000,,who overreached his station \Nand received your favor?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.36,0:03:24.12,Main,Ornis,0000,0000,0000,,Your supreme beauty is holy and absolute.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.12,0:03:26.35,Main,Ornis,0000,0000,0000,,It must never be sullied!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.35,0:03:29.39,Main,Ornis,0000,0000,0000,,Protecting it is my duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.68,0:03:31.88,Main,Hasegawa,0000,0000,0000,,Is that why you'd kill him?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.88,0:03:34.24,Main,Hasegawa,0000,0000,0000,,Like you did to the real Sakasaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.76,0:03:36.83,Main,Ornis,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.83,0:03:41.40,Main,Ornis,0000,0000,0000,,We are gods. Humans are just our\N eternal servants, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.87,0:03:44.91,Main,Hasegawa,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that Sakasaki was \Nthe lowest kind of scum.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.23,0:03:47.91,Main,Hasegawa,0000,0000,0000,,He laid his hands on female \Nstudents without discretion.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.91,0:03:50.52,Main,Hasegawa,0000,0000,0000,,He was the type who forced them \Nto accept it despite their tears.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.91,0:03:50.99,Flashback,Sakazaki,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wouldn't it be bad for you \Nif others find out about this?{\an8}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.52,0:03:52.92,Main,Hasegawa,0000,0000,0000,,So when you went after him...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.99,0:03:54.08,Flashback,Sakazaki,0000,0000,0000,,Then... you know what to do, right?{\an8}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.08,0:03:58.00,Flashback,Sakazaki,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. If you behave, \NI won't tell anyone.{\an8}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.08,0:03:59.25,Main,Hasegawa,0000,0000,0000,,I overlooked it out of \Nconsideration for a comrade.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.22,0:04:02.40,Main,Hasegawa,0000,0000,0000,,But this time, I can't \Noverlook what you've done.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.40,0:04:05.93,Main,Ornis,0000,0000,0000,,Why?! Why do you go so far?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.23,0:04:10.01,Main,Ornis,0000,0000,0000,,I-I cannot forgive those who would sully you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.43,0:04:12.57,Main,Ornis,0000,0000,0000,,Be they human, or worse—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.57,0:04:16.27,Main,Ornis,0000,0000,0000,,Those abominable, tainted fools!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.90,0:04:19.99,Main,Hasegawa,0000,0000,0000,,Watch your mouth, Ornis.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.99,0:04:23.03,Main,Hasegawa,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Her{\i0} blood flows within that child.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.48,0:04:26.16,Main,Hasegawa,0000,0000,0000,,I will not forgive anyone who \Nsoils the honor of her name,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.16,0:04:28.36,Main,Hasegawa,0000,0000,0000,,no matter who they might be.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.64,0:04:32.85,Main,Hasegawa,0000,0000,0000,,This child is the proof that she was alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.85,0:04:36.77,Main,Hasegawa,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do whatever it takes to protect him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.77,0:04:38.88,Main,Ornis,0000,0000,0000,,No, you can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.32,0:04:44.34,Main,Ornis,0000,0000,0000,,You can't continue sacrificing \Nyourself for this little brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.77,0:04:45.84,Main,Ornis,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.24,0:04:49.33,Main,Ornis,0000,0000,0000,,You should return with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.33,0:04:52.93,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,To Heaven! To those lofty heights!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.10,0:04:58.86,Main,Ornis,0000,0000,0000,,You can't stop this as you are now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.97,0:05:02.52,Main,Ornis,0000,0000,0000,,You sealed away most of your power
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.52,0:05:07.11,Main,Ornis,0000,0000,0000,,as the price for coming \Nto this world, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.49,0:05:08.73,Main,Ornis,0000,0000,0000,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.73,0:05:10.83,Main,Ornis,0000,0000,0000,,Toujou Basara!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.88,0:05:16.92,Main,Hasegawa,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that I underwent many judgments,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.04,0:05:20.52,Main,Hasegawa,0000,0000,0000,,especially from the other \Nmembers of the ten gods,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.52,0:05:24.92,Main,Hasegawa,0000,0000,0000,,but there were still a few who sided with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.37,0:05:28.72,Main,Hasegawa,0000,0000,0000,,I'm allowed to unleash the \Nsame power I once had
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.72,0:05:32.61,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,for one single purpose alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.60,0:05:34.43,Main,Ornis,0000,0000,0000,,You don't mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.80,0:05:35.69,Main,Hasegawa,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.17,0:05:39.08,Main,Hasegawa,0000,0000,0000,,When it's necessary to protect Basara,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.55,0:05:43.19,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,the seal on my power is temporarily lifted.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.33,0:05:49.98,Main,Ornis,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You're going to kill me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.98,0:05:52.12,Main,Ornis,0000,0000,0000,,If you truly want to protect Toujou,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.12,0:05:55.45,Main,Ornis,0000,0000,0000,,then it would've been better for you to \Nhave stood by quietly as he eliminated me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.81,0:06:00.96,Main,Afleia,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't stop Basara in order to save you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.23,0:06:02.07,Main,Ornis,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.07,0:06:05.92,Main,Afleia,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't afford to let Basara \Ncontinue running rampant.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.36,0:06:07.47,Main,Afleia,0000,0000,0000,,That was all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.87,0:06:11.48,Main,Afleia,0000,0000,0000,,And if a god like you is \Ninvolved in the matter,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.48,0:06:14.90,Main,Afleia,0000,0000,0000,,then someone like me who is not \Ninvolved with heroes or demons
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.90,0:06:17.48,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,ought to be the one to crush you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.96,0:06:20.48,Main,Afleia,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let anyone else handle it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.23,0:06:25.48,Main,Afleia,0000,0000,0000,,After using me yourself,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.77,0:06:29.41,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,you made Basara question me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.41,0:06:32.64,Main,Afleia,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to you, he even \Npointed his sword at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.10,0:06:35.24,Main,Afleia,0000,0000,0000,,How are you going to repay me for that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.61,0:06:37.25,Main,Afleia,0000,0000,0000,,Huh, Ornis?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.97,0:06:44.25,Main,Afleia,0000,0000,0000,,I'll stand in for Basara and \Neliminate every trace of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.50,0:06:49.51,Main,Ornis,0000,0000,0000,,A-Afleia-sama! I-I only did it for you—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.14,0:06:54.88,Main,Afleia,0000,0000,0000,,I certainly hope you aren't going to say
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.88,0:06:58.35,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,that was your attempt to beg for your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.00,0:07:04.68,Main,Afleia,0000,0000,0000,,Saying you harmed Basara for my sake
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.68,0:07:07.03,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,is practically begging me to kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.24,0:07:16.40,Main,Afleia,0000,0000,0000,,Brynhildr, I'll grant you the soul of \Nthe foolish one who tried to harm you,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.47,0:07:18.91,Main,Afleia,0000,0000,0000,,so make do with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.28,0:07:31.86,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,Mio, Yuki, Kurumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.44,0:07:33.93,Main,Hasegawa,0000,0000,0000,,You'd go this far for them?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.64,0:07:36.73,Main,Hasegawa,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a little jealous.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.52,0:07:43.94,Main,Hasegawa,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make it better now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.24,0:07:59.05,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.42,0:08:04.96,Main,Hasegawa,0000,0000,0000,,Now, Toujou, expel it all into me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.68,0:08:13.95,Main,Hasegawa,0000,0000,0000,,That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.95,0:08:15.97,Main,Hasegawa,0000,0000,0000,,Do as you please.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.20,0:08:30.18,Main,Hasegawa,0000,0000,0000,,Basara...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.74,0:08:35.00,Main,Hasegawa,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to alter some of your memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.00,0:08:37.60,Main,Hasegawa,0000,0000,0000,,About Ornis. About Sakasaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.24,0:08:40.67,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,About your loss of control. All of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.67,0:08:43.54,Main,Hasegawa,0000,0000,0000,,It's still too early for you to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.85,0:08:45.84,Main,Hasegawa,0000,0000,0000,,But one day...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.84,0:08:49.47,Main,Hasegawa,0000,0000,0000,,I look forward to being able to talk to you \Nabout everything that happened here today.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.12,0:08:54.22,Main,Hasegawa,0000,0000,0000,,About my true identity, and \Nabout the mother of both of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.00,0:09:20.24,Main,Tachibana,0000,0000,0000,,Long ago, our ancestors were driven \Nfrom our homeland by the hero clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.87,0:09:24.00,Main,Tachibana,0000,0000,0000,,There were some heroes who \Npurposely instigated things
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.00,0:09:26.58,Main,Tachibana,0000,0000,0000,,and blamed it on us vampires.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.55,0:09:32.00,Main,Tachibana,0000,0000,0000,,All so they could call us a dangerous species\N and cite that as a good reason to kill us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.23,0:09:33.96,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,That's what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.96,0:09:36.93,Main,Tachibana,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I thought you \Nwere here to destroy me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.73,0:09:39.16,Main,Tachibana,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Toujou-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.32,0:09:41.97,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing for you to apologize for.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.27,0:09:42.94,Main,Tachibana,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.94,0:09:48.28,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,Tachibana, even if the heroes\N targeted you for elimination,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.28,0:09:50.21,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,I would never do that to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.21,0:09:50.65,Main,Tachibana,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.11,0:09:53.65,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not a hero anymore, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.44,0:09:55.64,Main,Tachibana,0000,0000,0000,,Toujou-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.75,0:09:59.66,Italics,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,Tachibana wasn't at fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.36,0:10:02.20,Italics,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,The one who manipulated Donoue,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.20,0:10:05.07,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,who caused that twister, all of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.66,0:10:08.17,Italics,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,All of it was a trap set up by Sakasaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.80,0:10:10.50,Italics,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,I know I defeated him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.50,0:10:12.75,Italics,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,I can feel the reaction from Brynhildr,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.68,0:10:17.76,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,so why...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.56,0:10:23.20,Italics,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,Why does it feel like someone protected me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.20,0:10:24.89,Main,Maria,0000,0000,0000,,Basara-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.71,0:10:29.98,Main,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,Onii-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.98,0:10:31.31,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Basara...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.55,0:10:33.19,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You girls?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.32,0:10:35.97,Main,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,Basara-niichan...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.97,0:10:38.32,Main,Maria,0000,0000,0000,,Well, actually, you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.07,0:10:41.94,Flashback,Maria,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad everyone is safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.94,0:10:42.87,Flashback,Maria,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.36,0:10:48.58,Flashback,Maria,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like Mio-sama and the others \Nweren't of very much use this time around.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.58,0:10:50.36,Flashback,Maria,0000,0000,0000,,How troublesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.46,0:10:53.19,Main,Maria,0000,0000,0000,,Then after I told them that,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.19,0:10:57.69,Main,Maria,0000,0000,0000,,both of their pact curses \Nbegan to activate, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.69,0:10:58.76,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.28,0:11:02.68,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Then why is Kurumi in the same position?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.68,0:11:06.40,Main,Maria,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it wouldn't be\N nice to leave her out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.45,0:11:11.74,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,You did this on purpose! \NYou planned this, didn't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.74,0:11:14.20,Main,Maria,0000,0000,0000,,No way, it just turned out this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.20,0:11:15.77,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.17,0:11:18.46,Main,Maria,0000,0000,0000,,Going for clothed play in the bathroom?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.46,0:11:20.78,Main,Maria,0000,0000,0000,,Basara-san, you're quite the maniac.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.78,0:11:22.55,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,Who's the maniac here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.55,0:11:24.57,Main,Maria,0000,0000,0000,,Now, go on, Basara-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.73,0:11:28.30,Main,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.30,0:11:31.04,Main,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,Onii-chan, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.72,0:11:32.87,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.30,0:11:35.13,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,I'll relieve you right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.35,0:11:40.89,Main,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,Onii-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.31,0:11:49.07,Italics,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.07,0:11:50.24,Main,Maria,0000,0000,0000,,Basara-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.24,0:11:50.98,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.32,0:11:54.98,Main,Maria,0000,0000,0000,,Basara-san! If you'd like, use this!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.48,0:12:01.45,Main,Rukia,0000,0000,0000,,Maria, I heard you were behaving \Nwhile you're under house arrest?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.24,0:12:05.04,Main,Maria,0000,0000,0000,,Rukia-neesama?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.04,0:12:06.17,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,"Nee-sama"?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.57,0:12:10.71,Main,Rukia,0000,0000,0000,,I've come to convey the decision \Nof our moderate faction.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.71,0:12:14.32,Main,Rukia,0000,0000,0000,,We'd like to have all of you \Ncome to the demon realm with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.73,0:12:29.97,Main,Leohart,0000,0000,0000,,A relic of the demon wars\N waged in ancient times...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.39,0:12:33.39,Main,Leohart,0000,0000,0000,,Use it, and attack the moderate faction.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.39,0:12:36.23,Main,Leohart,0000,0000,0000,,That was the missive sent \Nto us by the council.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.86,0:12:43.95,Main,Balflear,0000,0000,0000,,The annoying ideas of the \Ncouncil nobles are nothing new,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.37,0:12:48.99,Main,Balflear,0000,0000,0000,,but ordering us to fight with a recently \Nuncovered relic we haven't properly analyzed yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.37,0:12:50.34,Main,Gald,0000,0000,0000,,Will you accept?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.93,0:12:52.25,Main,Leohart,0000,0000,0000,,I have no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.53,0:12:55.10,Main,Leohart,0000,0000,0000,,There's still the Jin Toujou \Nincident from the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.90,0:13:00.75,Main,Leohart,0000,0000,0000,,If they order me to regain the dignity \Nof the reigning Demon Lord's faction,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.44,0:13:03.04,Main,Leohart,0000,0000,0000,,I have no choice but to accept.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.66,0:13:15.08,Main,Leohart,0000,0000,0000,,Luka, how goes the analysis?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.28,0:13:16.92,Main,Leohart,0000,0000,0000,,Luka!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.92,0:13:18.40,Main,Luka,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.40,0:13:21.37,Main,Luka,0000,0000,0000,,I succeeded in releasing its seal,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.37,0:13:26.51,Main,Luka,0000,0000,0000,,but I've been having difficulty \Nundoing its previous pact of control.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.51,0:13:29.52,Main,Luka,0000,0000,0000,,It'll take a bit more time and adjustments \Nbefore you reforge a new pact with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.52,0:13:30.41,Main,Leohart,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.77,0:13:32.47,Main,Luka,0000,0000,0000,,My apologies.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.47,0:13:34.82,Main,Luka,0000,0000,0000,,I will be sure to make \Nthe reforging a success,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.82,0:13:37.07,Main,Luka,0000,0000,0000,,even if it costs me my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.07,0:13:38.42,Main,Leohart,0000,0000,0000,,Don't force yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.76,0:13:42.02,Main,Leohart,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't taken many breaks \Nhere in a while, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.48,0:13:44.92,Main,Leohart,0000,0000,0000,,I can't afford to have \Nyou collapse on me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.25,0:13:47.57,Main,Luka,0000,0000,0000,,No! Even if I happen to fall,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.57,0:13:50.41,Main,Luka,0000,0000,0000,,there are plenty of other \Nspecialized magicians!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.41,0:13:53.71,Main,Luka,0000,0000,0000,,I must finish this analysis \Nas soon as possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.27,0:13:56.00,Main,Gald,0000,0000,0000,,Don't misunderstand, Luka.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.03,0:13:58.95,Main,Gald,0000,0000,0000,,Other magicians have nothing to do with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.39,0:14:02.72,Main,Gald,0000,0000,0000,,You're the only magician Leohart trusts.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.72,0:14:04.27,Main,Gald,0000,0000,0000,,Be more cognizant of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.56,0:14:07.72,Main,Luka,0000,0000,0000,,Your Highness...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.46,0:14:20.50,Main,Balflear,0000,0000,0000,,The weapon aside, who's going \Nto take command of the assault?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.50,0:14:21.52,Main,Leohart,0000,0000,0000,,That...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.52,0:14:22.57,Main,Gald,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.28,0:14:25.17,Main,Leohart,0000,0000,0000,,Gald? But...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.17,0:14:28.65,Main,Gald,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need for you to go along \Nwith the council's recklessness.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.65,0:14:32.40,Main,Gald,0000,0000,0000,,Balflear should remain at \Nyour side as your aide.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.40,0:14:34.22,Main,Gald,0000,0000,0000,,I'm best suited for the role.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.22,0:14:36.22,Main,Leohart,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.01,0:14:40.80,Main,Leohart,0000,0000,0000,,You're the great general who \Nwas the sole survivor of
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.80,0:14:43.77,Main,Leohart,0000,0000,0000,,a duel with that war god who\N stirred up the demon general.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.77,0:14:48.86,Main,Leohart,0000,0000,0000,,You would have—No, you should \Nhave become the demon lord, yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.86,0:14:50.24,Main,Gald,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.61,0:14:55.15,Main,Gald,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to defeat the council that \Neven Wilbert couldn't completely purge
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.71,0:14:57.89,Main,Gald,0000,0000,0000,,and rebuild the demon \Nrealm from scratch, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.66,0:15:02.58,Main,Gald,0000,0000,0000,,I'll gladly lend you my \Nstrength for that cause.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.80,0:15:07.71,Main,Balflear,0000,0000,0000,,Now, all that remains is the question \Nof how to spin a just cause
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.71,0:15:10.18,Main,Balflear,0000,0000,0000,,in order to follow the council's \Nridiculous orders to attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.44,0:15:12.39,Main,Lars,0000,0000,0000,,That won't be a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.55,0:15:16.04,Main,Leohart,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, Lars?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.04,0:15:20.02,Main,Lars,0000,0000,0000,,The moderate faction has decided to summon \NNaruse Mio back to the demon realm.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.80,0:15:21.52,Main,Leohart,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.79,0:15:25.34,Main,Lars,0000,0000,0000,,It will finally be your chance to lay claim
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.34,0:15:28.03,Main,Lars,0000,0000,0000,,to the magic power Naruse \NMio inherited from Wilbert.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.61,0:15:29.92,Main,Leohart,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.92,0:15:32.29,Main,Leohart,0000,0000,0000,,Summoning the previous Demon Lord's daughter
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.29,0:15:35.24,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,is a clear act of aggression against us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.24,0:15:39.04,Main,Leohart,0000,0000,0000,,Eliminating that threat \Nwould serve as a reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.34,0:15:42.36,Main,Balflear,0000,0000,0000,,That's information worth ten thousand troops.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.96,0:15:45.09,Main,Balflear,0000,0000,0000,,If it's true, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.62,0:15:47.40,Main,Lars,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying you can't trust me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.20,0:15:51.38,Main,Lars,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess it's only natural to \Nquestion the word of a double agent
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.38,0:15:54.80,Main,Lars,0000,0000,0000,,who works for both the moderate faction \Nand the reigning Demon Lord's faction.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.08,0:15:56.62,Main,Balflear,0000,0000,0000,,Why, never.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.62,0:15:58.49,Main,Balflear,0000,0000,0000,,You're a comrade-in-arms \Nwho proved himself
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.49,0:16:02.29,Main,Balflear,0000,0000,0000,,by fighting alongside His \NHighness in the previous war.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.88,0:16:05.06,Main,Balflear,0000,0000,0000,,I just tend to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.72,0:16:08.21,Main,Lars,0000,0000,0000,,Well, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.32,0:16:18.40,Main,Rukia,0000,0000,0000,,Ramsus-sama, I've prepared your tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.22,0:16:20.08,Main,Ramsus,0000,0000,0000,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.09,0:16:22.08,Main,Rukia,0000,0000,0000,,As for that matter from the other day...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.68,0:16:24.84,Main,Rukia,0000,0000,0000,,I've received an official response.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.84,0:16:26.41,Main,Rukia,0000,0000,0000,,As soon as they prepare for the trip,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.41,0:16:28.28,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,they'll be coming to the demon realm.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.41,0:16:30.52,Main,Ramsus,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.52,0:16:33.59,Main,Rukia,0000,0000,0000,,I've also heard that an \Nassembly will be held soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.92,0:16:35.09,Main,Ramsus,0000,0000,0000,,An assembly?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.56,0:16:39.25,Main,Rukia,0000,0000,0000,,Claus-sama and the nobles \Naround him have called
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.25,0:16:42.60,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,for many to attend, regardless of class.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.24,0:16:45.89,Main,Rukia,0000,0000,0000,,He calls it a gathering of those \Nwho support His Highness, Wilbert.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.36,0:16:49.11,Main,Rukia,0000,0000,0000,,What shall we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.08,0:16:52.36,Main,Ramsus,0000,0000,0000,,Leave him alone. For now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.97,0:16:54.44,Main,Rukia,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.64,0:17:05.37,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,Go to the demon realm?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.74,0:17:07.38,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,For what purpose?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.38,0:17:08.88,Main,Rukia,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot say.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.30,0:17:11.75,Main,Rukia,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, I'm just a messenger.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.20,0:17:14.63,Main,Rukia,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not in a position to \Nexplain the circumstances.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.70,0:17:20.10,Main,Rukia,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure Ramsus-sama will explain the \Ndetails herself in the demon realm.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.83,0:17:22.14,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,Ramsus?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.51,0:17:24.48,Main,Rukia,0000,0000,0000,,The leader of the moderate faction,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.48,0:17:28.65,Main,Rukia,0000,0000,0000,,and the elder brother of our previous \NDemon Lord, His Majesty Wilbert.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.47,0:17:31.30,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,Wilbert's elder brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.66,0:17:43.16,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,What are you going to do, Mio?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.63,0:17:46.01,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,To be frank, I'm angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.64,0:17:51.17,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,It's far too cruel of them to summon \Nyou without giving any reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.60,0:17:53.20,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,I agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.20,0:17:55.31,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need to force ourselves to comply.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.31,0:17:58.01,Main,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,It's dangerous when you don't know \Nwhat the other party's after.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.17,0:18:02.18,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,But, if we turn it down arbitrarily,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.18,0:18:04.68,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,we'll probably drive a deep wedge \Nbetween us and the moderate faction.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.48,0:18:08.70,Main,Maria,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.39,0:18:13.07,Main,Maria,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what happens, \NI'll remain at Mio-sama's side.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.83,0:18:15.19,Main,Maria,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.78,0:18:17.75,Main,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,Maria.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.60,0:18:20.27,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,Same for me, Mio.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.05,0:18:24.63,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,All of us will protect you,l no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.63,0:18:28.08,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need to let yourself \Nbe driven by their desires.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.38,0:18:30.68,Main,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,Basara, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.68,0:18:31.86,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.35,0:18:34.59,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever happens, I'll accept it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.37,0:18:37.09,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,That's what family is, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.35,0:18:40.59,Main,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,Basara...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.11,0:18:45.10,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,Mio,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.49,0:18:47.10,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,what do you want to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.52,0:18:59.42,Main,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.44,0:19:08.12,Main,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go to the demon realm.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.64,0:19:11.51,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.19,0:19:14.38,Main,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly, I'm a little scared
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.98,0:19:18.42,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,of going somewhere I don't know \Nwithout understanding anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.74,0:19:21.69,Main,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm the former Demon Lord's daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.19,0:19:25.39,Main,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing will be resolved by backing down now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.89,0:19:26.67,Main,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.62,0:19:29.02,Main,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,So, I'm going.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.87,0:19:36.00,Main,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,It'll mean getting all of you \Ninvolved again, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.96,0:19:45.14,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,I said not to worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.14,0:19:46.08,Main,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,Basara...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.44,0:19:49.15,Main,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.72,0:19:50.84,Main,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.15,0:20:02.52,Italics,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,Father, Mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.40,0:20:05.52,Main,Kid,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.52,0:20:06.60,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Come here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.60,0:20:08.48,Main,Kid,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.06,0:20:10.81,Main,Kid,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.07,0:21:31.27,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, hold on! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.27,0:21:32.31,Main,Maria,0000,0000,0000,,Basara-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.31,0:21:33.72,Main,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Yuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.72,0:21:35.18,Main,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.08,0:21:37.15,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,Maria?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.57,0:21:39.07,Italics,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,I promise to come home.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.51,0:21:40.45,Italics,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,With everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.84,0:23:32.98,Main,Hasegawa,0000,0000,0000,,It's a good night to start a journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.14,0:23:39.98,Main,Screen,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(858,1)}Next Episode\N\N\N\N\NAmidst Entwining Plots
